name: &dPlayTime
lore:
&7This will import a &dPlaytime &cfunction&7 into your
&7house that can calculate the local players &aseconds&7,
&aminutes&7, and &ahours&7 played on your house!
&7It is also setup for global playtime/house uptime.

&7It uses &e%date.unix%&r&f to keep it accurate. &cShould be placed
&cinto a poison loop to work properly.
